{"pid":"cb761b5f7a7e1719f38867032498e58732ee05b3","tid":529483,"uid":162694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T21:59:37.000Z","msg":"Lexi doesn&rsquo;t die<br />\nThen she was very high<br />\nIf you want cry<br />\nFind a space to hide <br />\n<br />\n唔洗屌喇 係唔岩grammar嫁喇<br />\n只係諗起細個小學功課作過既野<br />\n大個睇到自己都覺得好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8ef5fd1fc8f0fb974f53f0da6d7e1860e8eb01","tid":529483,"uid":19978,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T22:01:11.000Z","msg":"入夢<br />\n<br />\n聽暗多少昏鴉暮嗚<br />\n唱擺幾許月下分離<br />\n方知山寺的鐘響了千載<br />\n原野的空，萬年不改<br />\n翕聚的耳鬢其實廝磨不了幾多個秋<br />\n<br />\n艄夫催渡，岸上的柳更青<br />\n劍客臨水，橋上的河激越<br />\n瞿然，驚見水中雙鯉，默默齧著故鄉的月<br />\n抽刀斷那滔滔。睚眥中，聽到你的呼喚<br />\n「我一定會等你」。埋頭，入夢<br />\n淚水，點滴成雨，滋潤了鈣化的魚目"},{"pid":"75c4d1652180988c258038c83aeab27272e28b5d","tid":529483,"uid":56393,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"48f8b164aff80caca22efa3f1d5e4ade4c02218c","tid":529483,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e580063553e8fff0ff7efed6876a86d15acf8890","tid":529483,"uid":34503,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1d7faa1ce1f75e16b24b4af2e1df77eb321ce95","tid":529483,"uid":46769,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T21:52:45.000Z","msg":"秋天秋天, <br />\n非常乾燥。 <br />\n有點寒冷,<br />\n最好燒烤。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T21:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T21:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T22:01:51.